sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor C as Customer
  participant M as Meta WhatsApp
  participant W as /api/whatsapp<br/>(HMAC verified)
  participant OB as Outbox + Worker
  participant A as AI agent<br/>(Kimi K2.6)
  participant FX as FX + Best-Rate<br/>Selection
  participant P as Pay page
  participant MC as Money engine
  participant PSP as Card / bank charger<br/>(mock today)
  participant SW as /api/payment-webhook<br/>(HMAC verified)
  participant R as Partner rail
  participant D as Dashboards

  C->>M: "Send $200 to Mom"
  M->>W: webhook (signed)
  W->>OB: enqueue agent.turn (wamid dedupe)
  OB->>A: drain → run turn
  A->>A: check_send_limit (tier caps, KYC gate)
  A->>FX: get_quote
  FX->>FX: live mid-market + partner rates<br/>strictly-better partner wins (rail checked)
  A->>M: Approve & Pay card (locked quote, 30-min draft)
  C->>P: tap → pay page
  P->>P: txn OTP + bank details (validated)
  P->>MC: finalize: claim-first idempotency →<br/>mint transfer (sanctions screened inside,<br/>draft quote honored)
  MC->>PSP: capture funding (idempotent by transfer id,<br/>blocked transfers are never charged)
  PSP-->>MC: captured
  MC->>MC: beginSettlement — ONE transaction:<br/>paid + stage-1 msg + rail effect
  MC->>OB: settlement.instruct (deduped)
  OB->>R: signed instruction<br/>(rail = best-rate winner ?? owner)
  R-->>SW: signed callback: paid_out
  SW->>MC: rank-guarded flip → delivered
  SW->>M: "Delivered ₹16,950" (owner branding) + recipient template<br/>— sent directly, best-effort (not outbox-queued)
  M->>C: confirmations
  MC->>D: live status via stamp polling:<br/>transactions, ops queues, compliance, tickets
  Note over MC,D: If stuck >15min: reconcile sweep re-instructs once + ops alert.<br/>If rejected in review: AUTO-REFUND via FundingProvider.<br/>Customer can ask the bot to refund a paid-not-delivered transfer.
